snippet.title: On Pathankot terror trail: Spot where cop's car was hijacked

localized.description:
NDTV retraces the route that Pathankot terrorists took and broadcasts from the spot where the Gurdaspur Superintendent of Police's car was hijacked. At this remote village of Kohlian, near the Indo-Pak border, the terrorists first dumped Ikagar Singh's taxi and then hijacked the cop's SUV - taking him, his jeweller friend and his cook hostage.

Watch more videos: http://www.ndtv.com/video?yt
